{"type": "article", "id": 47464, "title": "想要懒散躺一下，这把充气休闲椅是个好选择｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-11-21T23:30:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 544, "name": "巧克力"}, {"id": 40208, "name": "休闲椅"}, {"id": 45692, "name": "研磨瓶"}, {"id": 17906, "name": "毛绒玩具"}, {"id": 2263, "name": "台灯"}, {"id": 3562, "name": "卫浴产品"}, {"id": 45693, "name": "Pascalina Design Studio"}, {"id": 2291, "name": "Alessi"}, {"id": 15072, "name": "Vipp"}, {"id": 302, "name": "宜家"}, {"id": 43835, "name": "Hayden Martis"}, {"id": 23191, "name": "Yuta Takahashi"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 115, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171121175917DsZJkMylFgucnjYS.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} </style>  </p><h3>SAGOSKATT 索古斯卡限量系列 by IKEA</h3><p>宜家连续第三年举办毛绒玩具绘画比赛，邀请世界各地的儿童画出他们梦想的毛绒玩具。最终宜家选出 10 个最为独特的创意并将它们制成真实的毛绒玩具，组成宜家 SAGOSKATT 索古斯卡限量系列。10 位优胜者的创意包括无爪河马鳄鱼、带彩虹翅膀的独角腊肠犬、笑脸彩虹云、名叫“老虎”的狮子，以及其他六个新颖独特的形象。孩子们将颜色、形态和表达方式按照自己的个性结合起来。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121180604SAXjRBrMdCfbvygq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121180605DjlGtJLAkWq9ob2Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121180607utXyKWfUz8Jrm5Cv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711211806108vOkPGq2Nlgiozcu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：IKEA</figcaption></figure></div><h3>Mandarin natural Chocolate by Yuta Takahashi</h3><p>这款名为 Mandarin 的天然巧克力包装，关键信息集中于可可浓度，通过 10 个小圆点形成的梯度结构来显示每款巧克力的可可浓度，比如60%、80%或100%。</p><p>这个封面创意来自日本艺术家 Yuta Takahashi，包装简约干净，专注于穿搭产品本身的关键信息，是一个将简约优雅与现代印象融为一体的包装佳作，也试图带给顾客新的品牌体验。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121180654S3LkgCVxTINPd6os.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121180658NlOXs5qUR309xdZ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121180658gHrRJZeqTa19w5uv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121180700IHU6sEMnPTzNeDL5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121180700eVUd9nJruCsihz0B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121180701XRlfitMuBkayeNOK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yutatakahashi.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yuta Takahashi</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Ascension Lamp by Hayden Martis</h3><p>说实话，要找到合适的词来形容伦敦设计师 Hayden Martis 的这款灯，有点困难。设计师本身已经用一个简单但非常精确的句子来捕捉灯的整个概念和感觉：通过光线表现空间中的运动感。</p><p>当你仔细观察这盏灯时，你会理解这句话。它使用的材料很少，试图表达的东西却很多。细长的圆柱体延展向上，肆意生长的线条在到达顶端时让光线蔓延开来。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121180752L5hdg3v6b8DiEUBx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121180753O29vTtyxhZiEmwIY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121180753ufxL7JAwn4a0oW3T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121180754xGzaCjJZK71ytTEq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.haydenmartis.com/projects/ascension\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hayden Martis</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Bathroom Collection by Vipp</h3><p>丹麦高端设计品牌 Vipp 以生产厨房和卫浴产品闻名，在这套卫浴系列作品中，设计师始终坚持着品牌一直以来的偏好和纯粹特性，在黑色和白色之间变化出各种复杂性。</p><p>圆滑的边角使得设计表达中的细节变得重要，没见作品的设计都是以强化功能为重要目的，省去了任何不必要的细节。它并不参考纯粹的几何形状，但最终实现的效果却很摩登。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711211808462Eicgah7Inx5p3RB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.803340\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121180846T8MvehuB2SjdcAaD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.859333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121180846qrGI4ZD1LJRi6ES7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121180848Zkl6Hr9FzBexoALY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.859333\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711211808505I2UpBQcEJ1CakYW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Vipp</figcaption></figure></div><h3>Salt, pepper and spice grinder Grind by William Alsop &amp; Federico Grazzini</h3><p>意大利厨具设计品牌 Alessi 这一季的秋冬新品中，一款海盐胡椒研磨瓶看着很有趣。这是设计师 William Alsop 和 Federico Grazzini 的合力制作，两人不仅想要赋予这款日常小物丰富的艺术表现力，还想让其成为餐桌上的优雅角色。一条条紧密排列的褶皱包裹着整个瓶身，平常竖立于桌面上就是一个小装饰，使用时将顶部的研磨机倒置便可。提供铝质和黑色两种选择，售价 125 美元，<a href=\"https://www.alessi.com/us_en/product/fall-winter-2017/grind.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711211809397AunfUkYsy0ijX6I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.860606\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121180942RBmCMnqi9fF3cuIO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.977876\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121180942D39uOopdL4HgevF7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.885602\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121180943LMNqG0K6uvyFSX5n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.670913\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.alessi.com/us_en/product/fall-winter-2017/grind.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alessi</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Beach Cocoon by Pascalina Design Studio</h3><p>Beach Cocoon 是一个充气休闲椅，来自比利时设计工作室 Pascalina 的新作。他们设想的使用场景可以在沙滩、游泳池、花园、露台、房子、酒店或是活动现场。它用一个鼓风机 5 分钟即可充好，内部的空气可以很好地适应身体的结构而动，比懒人沙发更舒服。售价 988 美元，目前可提供 5 折起的折扣，可联系 info@pascalina.be。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121181028hkxytOBjmCEdsriZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665557\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121181029YXi1prdHtnLeIV0c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669537\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121181029IwSXRMjszLxhbTZy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171121181029QDJmzMiSEo6vhpny.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.pascalina.be/#/beach-cocoon/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pascalina Design Studio</a></p>"}